;Mozilla Advocacy
Aɣnas


;Rallying citizens to protect the open Internet
Sdukel iɣermanen akken ad ḥerzen Web yeldin


;Mozilla’s advocacy engine works with allies to cultivate a global force of tens of millions of people, who are aware of the issues that are vital to the future of the open Internet and prepared to take action in support of the rights of citizens of the web.
Mozilla txeddem lwaḥid akked imendiden-is akken ad tsebges imrawen n imelyan n imdanen deg umaḍal, i yeẓran d acu yellan deffir neɣ ayen ara d-yawi Web yeldin, d wid iheggan ad seḥbibren ɣef izerfan n iɣermanen n Web.


;We are dedicated to building a world where:
Aqlaɣ dagi akken ad nebnu amaḍal anida:


;People are making more conscious choices to build and protect the open Internet
Imdanen fernen s tmusni akken ad bnun neɣ ad ḥarben ɣef Internet yeldin


;Companies and governments create products, policies and laws to support the open Internet because of public pressure to do so
Tikebbaniyin akked inabaḍen snulfuyen-d ifarisenn tisertityin akked isuḍaf akken ad mudden afus i Internet yeldin imi imdanen suturen-d aya


;How we work: A focus on depth and scale
Amahil nneɣ: d usdid, d amaḍalan


;Mozilla’s advocacy approach incorporates both scale to depth and depth to scale to properly address the diversity of issues that we work on.
Anmeqqen ameɣnas n Mozilla seg iwen n idis d amaḍalan, seg wayeḍ d adigan, ayagi aɣ-yeǧǧ ad nexdem ɣef isental meṛṛa i nebɣa seg ul.


;This approach enables Mozilla to simultaneously build our capacity to mobilize millions of people quickly and grow our organizing power in local communities, which will make it possible to win on our issues in the long-term.
Tarrayt-agi ad tsireg i Mozilla ad tesnifel tazmert-is akken ad tsebges imelyan n imdanen s zreb, acu kan daɣen, ad tessali tazmert n usuddes di tmezdagnutin tidiganin, ihi ad nizmir ad d-nerbeḥ amennuɣ ar zdat.


;We also push ourselves to be proactive — setting the topic and tone of the conversation, and promoting solutions — as well as reactive to current events or undesirable policies when necessary.
Nettaɛraḍ ad nheggi send ad d-ḍrunt — ad d-nessers asentel akked tiqqrit n useqerdec, udiɣ ad d-nheggi tifrat — maca ula d tiririt i wayen d-iḍerrun d amaynut neɣ i yir tsertiyin  ticki ilaq.


;Our initiatives
Izwuren-nneɣ


;Mozilla’s Advocacy Engine consists of five key initiatives:
Asenfaṛ Advocacy n Mozilla yegber semmus n yizwuren:


;Campaigns.
Imzizzel.


;Our campaigns amplify the Mozilla community’s collective voice, in order to address the issues we believe must be tackled in the current era to build the open Internet we want. Example: <a href="%(url_encrypt_campaign)s">Encrypt</a>
Imzizzal-nneɣ n teywalt refden taɣect n tmezdagnut n Mozilla, ayagi aɣ-yeǧǧ ad nger afus deg uguren n tura akken ad nebnu Internet yeldin, akken nella nekni. Amedya, <a href="%(url_encrypt_campaign)s">Awgelhen</a>.


;Online.
Di Web.


;Naturally, the pulse of the movement to protect the open Internet lives on the web. We nurture a strong online community with a bias toward action, and drive mass digital mobilization behind our campaigns.
Nuɣ tanumi d akken ul n umussu yemmestanen Internet yeldin yekkat ɣef Web. Nsenned ɣef tmezdagnut iǧehden srdi, yerran lewhi ar tigawt, nesdukel timeɣnest tumḍint tamaḍalant deg imzizzal-nneq.


;Media.
Taγwalt.


;We tell creative, compelling stories that bring the biggest challenges and opportunities facing the open Internet to life, and into the mainstream.
Ameslay ɣef tɣawsiwin s wudem n usnulfu akken timeɣnest aɣ-yessireg ad nzuzer i ddeqs n yimdanen s wudem uddir, icqirrwen i yettmager Internet akked d wayen i d-yettmuddu.


;Field.
Urti.


;We connect, support and amplify the work of technologists, policy wonks, artists and activists committed to helping shape and drive Mozilla’s campaigns.
Nteqqen, nettmuddu afus nessemɣeṛ amahil n imestekniyen, wid iḥemlen tasertit, in,aẓuren akken imeɣnasen yesseḥbibirel ɣef ufeṣṣel akked uɛiwen di Mozilla.


;Infrastructure and networks.
Tadumṣuka akked iẓedwa.


;The foundation that supports and drives our advocacy work, by bringing together awesome people, organizations and technology to fuel our campaigns and the wider movement. Example: <a href="%(url_owf)s">Open Web Fellows</a>
S usdukel n yimdanen, tuddsiwin akked titiknulujiyin ifazen, tasbeddit ad tesireg i umzizzel n teywalt akked umussu-nneɣ ad aẓen ar zdat. Ayagi ad yessiǧhed amennuɣ-nneɣ am akken i t-id-skanen <a href="%(url_owf)s">Iɛeggalen n Web yeldin</a>.


